claim.claim-text:
A tire manufacturing method for manufacturing the tire of any one of claim 1 to claim 5 using the tire manufacturing apparatus of claim 6, the tire manufacturing method comprising:
engaging the engagement section with the support engagement section;
adding a resin material and joining the pair of tire frame halves;
retracting the leading end portions of the arm sections to the tire radial direction inner side and separating the leading end portions of the arm sections from the tire support member; and
removing the tire support member from the inner side of the tire frame halves.
